<h3>Madrilla Password Reset Request</h3>
<p>
Dear <%= @user.name %>
</p>

<p>
We received a request to reset the password associated with this email
address, <%= @user.email %>. You may reset your password by clicking on
the link below. If you did not request a password reset, you may
simply ignore this email message.
</p>
<p>
	Click here to reset your password:
	<%= link_to recover_url(@user.reset_code), recover_url(@user.reset_code) %>
</p>


